{"tid":623963,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"連登有無人打天九？","createTime":"2018-04-10T11:57:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-29T11:24:38.000Z","uid":91936,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"4d72ec215077834620454a9125e041b829e62eca","tid":623963,"uid":91936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/_s4IYWuw5YUc/SceK7TQFmGI/AAAAAAAAAsY/wPujosxvcks/s1600-h/heaven_nine1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F_s4IYWuw5YUc%2FSceK7TQFmGI%2FAAAAAAAAAsY%2FwPujosxvcks%2Fs1600-h%2Fheaven_nine1.png&h=309d991f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n天九是從宋徽宗宣和年間產生的骨牌宣和牌演化而成的。一般人都認為打天九只是一個純粹賭博的遊戲，<span style=\"color: red;\">那是因為大部分人都將天九與牌九混為一談。</span>天九其實是一個講求思考、記性、運氣和捉心理的遊戲；其玩法有少許像鋤大D和橋牌，但天九就更多變及複雜。<br />\n天九與牌九用的牌幾乎一樣，但天九用的較厚，而牌九用的則較薄；天九牌亦可用作玩斜釘之用。天九牌一般四個人玩。<br />\n<br />\n年幾前fd教咗我玩之後玩到唔停手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係香港幾乎見唔到人打天九<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無巴絲識打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b19094c27c3ecd0cea03695249a76cec07c2e2b","tid":623963,"uid":91936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:58:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/195842_8742ad2f05a2921a637f8f1b42efe806.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F195842_8742ad2f05a2921a637f8f1b42efe806.png&h=c132de1b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9e794120cdcd0641e55317de313ace9590cf65af","tid":623963,"uid":27743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"打馬屌"},{"pid":"6fa2f694239ee3748abba29cf44e7e